TOPIC
	General man page for coders

Important man pages:

	You should read all these, and check them now and then
	for possible changes.

    Rules

	coder_law	General coder rules.
	control		Rules about coder-controlled monsters.
	guilcoders	Rules about guildcoders.
	promotion	Rules about coder promotions.

    Building

	armours		Armour balance rules. These must be followed.
	monsters	NPC/Monster balance rules.
	weapons		Weapon balance rules, likewise.

	For building documents, the best place to start is to
	cd into /doc/NEW_DOCS and read the documents there. They
	are the most recent ones.

